 "PsZUA", "name": "CardHeader", "type": "frame", "width": "fill_container"}, {"children": [{"content": "运维主管王工私下提到团队运维能力有限,希望系统能傻瓜式运维,最好有自动告警和一键恢复功能。这暗示运维自动化程度将成为隐性评判标准。", "fill": "#595959", "fontFamily": "Inter", "fontSize": 13, "id": "wlmsT", "lineHeight": 1.8, "textGrowth": "fixed-width", "type": "text", "width": "fill_container"}, {"children": [{"content": "AI 推理", "fill": "#1677FF", "fontFamily": "Inter", "fontSize": 11, "fontWeight": "500", "id": "pZ6Fw", "type": "text"}], "cornerRadius": 3, "fill": "#F0F5FF", "id": "GbngB", "name": "aiTag3", "padding": [1, 6], "type": "frame"}], "cornerRadius": 4, "fill": "#FAFAFA", "gap": 8, "id": "Tqi2s", "layout": "vertical", "name": "ReasoningArea", "padding": 12, "stroke": {"align": "inside", "fill": "#E8E8E8", "thickness": {"left": 4}}, "type": "frame", "width": "fill_container"}, {"children": [{"fill": "#FAAD14", "height": 16, "iconFontFamily": "lucide", "iconFontName": "lightbulb", "id": "h1kWs", "type": "icon_font", "width": 16}, {"content": "方案运维章节需突出智能运维平台能力,展示自动巡检、告警推送、一键故障恢复等功能截图和操作流程。", "fill": "#262626", "fontFamily": "Inter", "fontSize": 13, "id": "gqrnM", "lineHeight": 1.6, "textGrowth": "fixed-width", "type": "text", "width": "fill_container"}], "gap": 8, "id": "hNul2", "name": "SuggestionArea", "type": "frame", "width": "fill_container"}, {"children": [{"alignItems": "center", "children": [{"fill": "#52C41A", "height": 13, "iconFontFamily": "lucide", "iconFontName": "check", "id": "GOjGf", "type": "icon_font", "width": 13}, {"content": "确认", "fill": "#52C41A", "fontFamily": "Inter", "fontSize": 12, "fontWeight": "500", "id": "E1O5Y", "type": "text"}], "cornerRadius": 4, "fill": "#F6FFED", "gap": 4, "id": "lQxlS", "name": "confirmBtn", "padding": [4, 12], "type": "frame"}, {"alignItems": "center", "children": [{"fill": "#A1A1AA", "height": 13, "iconFontFamily": "lucide", "iconFontName": "pencil", "id": "58j0Z", "type": "icon_font", "width": 13}, {"content": "编辑", "fill": "#A1A1AA", "fontFamily": "Inter", "fo